      <title>mysql中表操作</title>
      <link href="2021/01/24/biao-cao-zuo/"/>
      <url>2021/01/24/biao-cao-zuo/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>创建表</p></blockquote><p>​    create table 表名称(字段名称 字段类型(长度) 约束,字段名称 字段类型(长度) 约束…);</p><hr><blockquote><p>字段类型</p></blockquote><table><thead><tr><th>java</th><th>mysql</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>byte/short/int/long</td><td>tinyint/smallint/int/bigint</td></tr><tr><td>float</td><td>float</td></tr><tr><td>double</td><td>double</td></tr><tr><td>boolean</td><td>bit</td></tr><tr><td>char/String</td><td>char/varchar</td></tr><tr><td>Data</td><td>datatime/timestamp</td></tr><tr><td>File</td><td>BLOB/TEXT</td></tr></tbody></table><p><img src="C:\Users\27329\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20210124100116406.png" alt="image-20210124100116406"></p><blockquote><p>约束</p></blockquote><p>​    单表约束</p><ul><li><p>主键约束 primary key </p><p>​                默认唯一，非空</p></li><li><p>唯一约束 unique</p></li><li><p>非空约束 not null</p></li></ul><hr><blockquote></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
      
